==Nature== Belapur is surrounded by greenery<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/more-lifestyle/check-out-these-secret-monsoon-havens-right-here-in-mumbai/story-gvjC4UXDCL5XuzbjMc8vMJ.html|work=[[Hindustan Times]]|title=Check-out these secret monsoon havens, right here in Mumbai|last=Anesha George|access-date=19 October 2017|date=13 August 2016}}</ref>and it is much more organized than other parts of Navi Mumbai.{{clarify|date=April 2017}} There are a couple of waterfalls situated in sector 8B, where people come for treking and nature trails. There are other open spaces in and around Belapur.{{fact|date=April 2017}}
== Nightlife == Belapur has a variety of options in the nightlife, and it is crowded with lounges of Navi Mumbai.{{fact|date=April 2017}} In sector-15 near the Hotel Nimantran they have [http://www.rudelounge.co.in/location-belapur.html Rude].{{fact|date=April 2017}} There are new cafes which have open up like Roasted bean cafe, The Vintage Cafe, The Smoque Cafe and if you are a Tea lover then you should try Chaai Centre.
==Shopping and Eating== For sports enthusiast Decathlon one of the leading sports outlets has come up with its store in Sector-15 of Belapur which is surrounded by Stores like Nike, Adidas, Woodland & one of the world famous fast food chains i.e. Mc Donald's & Burger King. EDUCATION:- *bharti vidyapeeth institute ,cbd belapur *Dr.d y high school & junior college,belapur
==Law and order==
The office of police commissioner Of Navi Mumbai is at CBD Belapur Sector 10. A police station is also at sector 1.
